(197, 'Asus AI Noise-Canceling USB-C to 3.5 mm Mic Adapter', 'admin', 1, 7, NULL, NULL, NULL, '400', '400', 'youtube', NULL, 'Asus AI Noise,Canceling USB-C to 3.5 mm Mic Adapter', '<ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Model: AI Noise-Canceling</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">AI-powered noise‑canceling technology</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Asus Hyper-Grounding technology</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Lightweight and compact design</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">USB-C and USB 2.0 connectors</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\"><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; line-height: 26px;\">Asus AI Noise-Canceling USB-C to 3.5 mm Mic Adapter</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">The Asus AI Noise-Canceling USB-C to 3.5 mm Mic Adapter is a well rounded audio accessory that helps to provide you with the best audio output for your enjoyment. The Asus AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter enhances the quality of your audio greatly and lets you experience audio in a whole different level from before. Raising the bar of audio entertainment high, the Asus AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter is able to do all.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">ASUS AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">ASUS AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter is the world\'s first USB-C-to-3.5 mm adapter with integrated AI Noise-Canceling Microphone (AI Mic) technology. It uses AI-powered noise cancelation to deliver crystal clear voice communication when used with any 3.5 mm headset with a microphone. Weighing just 8 grams, it includes a digital-to-analogue converter (DAC) that includes exclusive ASUS Hyper-Grounding technology to prevent electromagnetic interference, giving you noise-free audio. Get a big upgrade on sound quality with this small device.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">AI Noise-Canceling Technology<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">ASUS AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter uses the power of AI to enhance headset communication. A processor loaded with AI-enhanced profiles reduces over 500 millions types of background noise while preserving vocal harmonics, so you can enjoy crystal-clear voice communication in any environment.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Maximizing Performance<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">ASUS AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter works with any 3.5 mm headset that includes a microphone. For best results, pair your headphones with a laptop featuring a unidirectional microphone. The Asus AI Noise-Canceling USB-C to 3.5 mm Mic Adapter has 1 Year Warranty.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Embedded chipset<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">The chipset that powers the AI technology is located in the adapter itself, so use of the adapter won\'t affect the performance of your PC or laptop. Simply plug it in to any device to enjoy clear communication in almost any scenario.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Pure audio quality<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">The integrated 96 kHz / 24-bit DAC features exclusive ASUS Hyper-Grounding technology that prevents electromagnetic interference via a multilayer PCB and special layout design, resulting in pristine audio that\'s free of EMI noise.</p></li></ul>', 3300.00, 3300.00, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '1 Pcs', 1, 1, 0.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, 'free', '0', 0, NULL, 0, 'Asus AI Noise-Canceling USB-C to 3.5 mm Mic Adapter', 'Model: AI Noise-CancelingAI-powered noise‑canceling technologyAsus Hyper-Grounding technologyLightweight and compact designUSB-C and USB 2.0 connectorsAsus AI Noise-Canceling USB-C to 3.5 mm Mic AdapterThe Asus AI Noise-Canceling USB-C to 3.5 mm Mic Adapter is a well rounded audio accessory that helps to provide you with the best audio output for your enjoyment. The Asus AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter enhances the quality of your audio greatly and lets you experience audio in a whole different level from before. Raising the bar of audio entertainment high, the Asus AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter is able to do all.ASUS AI Noise-Canceling Mic AdapterASUS AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter is the world\'s first USB-C-to-3.5 mm adapter with integrated AI Noise-Canceling Microphone (AI Mic) technology. It uses AI-powered noise cancelation to deliver crystal clear voice communication when used with any 3.5 mm headset with a microphone. Weighing just 8 grams, it includes a digital-to-analogue converter (DAC) that includes exclusive ASUS Hyper-Grounding technology to prevent electromagnetic interference, giving you noise-free audio. Get a big upgrade on sound quality with this small device.AI Noise-Canceling TechnologyASUS AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter uses the power of AI to enhance headset communication. A processor loaded with AI-enhanced profiles reduces over 500 millions types of background noise while preserving vocal harmonics, so you can enjoy crystal-clear voice communication in any environment.Maximizing PerformanceASUS AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter works with any 3.5 mm headset that includes a microphone. For best results, pair your headphones with a laptop featuring a unidirectional microphone. The Asus AI Noise-Canceling USB-C to 3.5 mm Mic Adapter has 1 Year Warranty.Embedded chipsetThe chipset that powers the AI technology is located in the adapter itself, so use of the adapter won\'t affect the performance of your PC or laptop. Simply plug it in to any device to enjoy clear communication in almost any scenario.Pure audio qualityThe integrated 96 kHz / 24-bit DAC features exclusive ASUS Hyper-Grounding technology that prevents electromagnetic interference via a multilayer PCB and special layout design, resulting in pristine audio that\'s free of EMI noise.', '400', NULL, 'Asus-AI-Noise-Canceling-USB-C-to-35-mm-Mic-Adapter-sSQBx', 1, 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-06 05:47:46', '2021-07-06 05:47:46'),
(198, 'ASUS C3 Streaming Kits Webcam', 'admin', 1, 7, NULL, NULL, NULL, '401', '401', 'youtube', NULL, 'ASUS C3 Streaming Kits Webcam', '<h2 style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Key Features</h2><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Model: C3</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Compatible with Skype, Microsoft Teams and Zoom</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Sharp FHD (1920 x 1080)</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Crystal-Clear Video Calls</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">90° Tilt‑Adjustable Clip</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\"><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; line-height: 26px;\">ASUS C3 Streaming Kits Webcam</h2><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Enjoy Sharper Video Calls<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">Enjoy sharper, smoother video streaming and crystal-clear audio with ASUS Webcam. Delivering crisp and detailed FHD (1920 x 1080) video in a widescreen format, ASUS Webcam can be connected via USB and placed anywhere on your desk or on top of your monitor. A 360° rotation mechanism ensures flexibility for any camera angle, and a built-in beamforming microphone array ensures loud and