(198, 197, 'Asus AI Noise-Canceling USB-C to 3.5 mm Mic Adapter', '1 Pcs', '<ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Model: AI Noise-Canceling</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">AI-powered noise‑canceling technology</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Asus Hyper-Grounding technology</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Lightweight and compact design</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">USB-C and USB 2.0 connectors</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\"><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; line-height: 26px;\">Asus AI Noise-Canceling USB-C to 3.5 mm Mic Adapter</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">The Asus AI Noise-Canceling USB-C to 3.5 mm Mic Adapter is a well rounded audio accessory that helps to provide you with the best audio output for your enjoyment. The Asus AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter enhances the quality of your audio greatly and lets you experience audio in a whole different level from before. Raising the bar of audio entertainment high, the Asus AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter is able to do all.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">ASUS AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">ASUS AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter is the world\'s first USB-C-to-3.5 mm adapter with integrated AI Noise-Canceling Microphone (AI Mic) technology. It uses AI-powered noise cancelation to deliver crystal clear voice communication when used with any 3.5 mm headset with a microphone. Weighing just 8 grams, it includes a digital-to-analogue converter (DAC) that includes exclusive ASUS Hyper-Grounding technology to prevent electromagnetic interference, giving you noise-free audio. Get a big upgrade on sound quality with this small device.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">AI Noise-Canceling Technology<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">ASUS AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter uses the power of AI to enhance headset communication. A processor loaded with AI-enhanced profiles reduces over 500 millions types of background noise while preserving vocal harmonics, so you can enjoy crystal-clear voice communication in any environment.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Maximizing Performance<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">ASUS AI Noise-Canceling Mic Adapter works with any 3.5 mm headset that includes a microphone. For best results, pair your headphones with a laptop featuring a unidirectional microphone. The Asus AI Noise-Canceling USB-C to 3.5 mm Mic Adapter has 1 Year Warranty.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Embedded chipset<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">The chipset that powers the AI technology is located in the adapter itself, so use of the adapter won\'t affect the performance of your PC or laptop. Simply plug it in to any device to enjoy clear communication in almost any scenario.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Pure audio quality<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">The integrated 96 kHz / 24-bit DAC features exclusive ASUS Hyper-Grounding technology that prevents electromagnetic interference via a multilayer PCB and special layout design, resulting in pristine audio that\'s free of EMI noise.</p></li></ul>', 'en', '2021-07-06 05:47:46', '2021-07-06 05:47:46'),
(199, 198, 'ASUS C3 Streaming Kits Webcam', '1 Pcs', '<h2 style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Key Features</h2><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Model: C3</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Compatible with Skype, Microsoft Teams and Zoom</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Sharp FHD (1920 x 1080)</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Crystal-Clear Video Calls</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">90° Tilt‑Adjustable Clip</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\"><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; line-height: 26px;\">ASUS C3 Streaming Kits Webcam</h2><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Enjoy Sharper Video Calls<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">Enjoy sharper, smoother video streaming and crystal-clear audio with ASUS Webcam. Delivering crisp and detailed FHD (1920 x 1080) video in a widescreen format, ASUS Webcam can be connected via USB and placed anywhere on your desk or on top of your monitor. A 360° rotation mechanism ensures flexibility for any camera angle, and a built-in beamforming microphone array ensures loud and clear audio.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Sharp and Smooth FHD Streaming<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">Enjoy high-resolution 1080p video calls and streams at a buttery-smooth 30 frames per second.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Wider Field of View<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">The wide angle lens captures more, making ASUS Webcam perfect for conferences, telecommuting, or chats with two or more parties sitting side-by-side.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Beamforming Mic for Clearer Audio<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">ASUS Webcam C3 features two built-in microphones with beamforming technology to filter out ambient noise such as fan whir, keyboard clicks, in-game sounds and voices other than your own — so you’ll always come in loud and clear.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Adjustable Clip for Different Devices<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">The 90° tilt‑adjustable clip fits a variety of laptop screens and desktop monitors, and it rotates 360° for more flexible placement options.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Broad Compatibility<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">ASUS Webcam C3 is compatible with PC, Mac, and Chrome OS. It’s the ideal solution for video conferencing, video calls or eLearning.</p></li></ul>', 'en', '2021-07-06 05:50:05', '2021-07-06 05:50:05'),
(200, 199, 'Asus ROG Strix Arion Lite M.2 SSD Enclosure', '1 Pcs', '<h2 style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Key Features</h2><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Model: ROG Strix Arion Lite</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Supports M.2 PCIe NVM Express SSD</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Futuristic design with Aura Sync</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Speeds of up to 10 Gbps</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">USB-C 3.2 Gen 2</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\"><section class=\"description bg-white m-tb-15\" id=\"description\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 20px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 1px 1px;\"><div class=\"full-description\" itemprop=\"description\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px;\"><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; line-height: 26px;\">Asus ROG Strix Arion Lite M.2 SSD Enclosure</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">The Asus ROG Strix Arion Lite M.2 SSD Enclosure is a very advance technology from Asus which lets you connect your high speed M.2 SSD drive to it and carry it around anywhere easily. This allows you to take your secured files and other data easily and efficiently. The Asus ROG Strix Arion Lite Enclosure has built-in heat pads that help to dissipate heat very quickly and efficiently. The Asus ROG Strix Arion Lite Enclosure also has RGB lighting system built into it for more visual expect. The Aluminum casing of the device products it from any unwanted drops or damages. The Asus ROG Strix Arion Lite M.2 SSD Enclosure has 1 Year Warranty.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Stay Cool, Stay Fast<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">ROG Strix Arion Lite is an SSD enclosure that fits an M.2 PCIe NVM Express SSD with a 2230/ 2242/ 2260/ 2280 form factor and features USB-C 3.2 Gen 2 connectivity to deliver data transfer speeds of up to 10 Gbps. Its sleek aluminum alloy case features thermal pads for excellent heat dissipation and exclusive ASUS Aura Sync lighting effects that altogether make ROG Strix Arion Lite a high-performance, mobile storage solution.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Support M.2 PCIe NVM Express SSD<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">ROG Strix Arion Lite does not support SATA-based B key/ B+M Key and PCIe/ ACHI-based M key. ROG Strix Arion Lite currently does not support Micron P5 SSD and Realtek RTS5765DL/ RTS5766DL controllers, such as but not limited to ADATA SWORDFISH and ADATA XPG SPECTRIX S20G.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Aggressive heat dissipation<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">An aluminum alloy case with included thermal pads reduce operating temperatures drastically, enabling your SSD to maintain high transfer speeds and extending its longevity.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Innovative screwdriver-free installation<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">ROG Strix Arion Lite features a pin-design and thumbscrew-installation system that makes it easy to mount your SSD into the enclosure. No screwdriver is required.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">USB-C to C cable<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">ROG Strix Arion Lite comes with USB-C to USB-C cable for greater convenience and compatibility with a wide range of devices, including laptops, smartphones, PC, and gaming consoles.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">ASUS Aura Sync lighting effects<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">With exclusive ASUS Aura Sync lighting technology, ROG Strix Arion Lite provides ambient lighting that perfectly complements your gaming rig for true expression of your individuality.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></div></section><section class=\"latest-price bg-white m-tb-15\" id=\"latest-price\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 20px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 1px 1px;\"><div class=\"section-head\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px;\"></div></section></li></ul>', 'en', '2021-07-06 05:53:22', '2021-07-06 05:53:22'),
(201, 200, 'Baseus Steel Cannon Series USB A Gigabit LAN Adapter', '1 Pcs', '<h2 style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Key Features</h2><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">MPN: CAHUB-AD0G</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Model: Steel Cannon Series</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Body material: Aluminum</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Connection interface: USB-A</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Connectors: Ethernet</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Data rate: 1Gbps</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\"><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; line-height: 26px; text-align: justify;\">Baseus Steel Cannon Series Gigabit LAN Adapter</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify;\">Expand the Ethernet port for notebook computers, and solve the problem that conventional notebook computers do not have RJ45 interfaces. By connecting a USB hub to a PC or laptop, you get an additional RJ-45 Ethernet connector supporting data transfer rates up to 1 Gbps. The housing of the hub is compact and made of aluminum alloy. It supports plug and play, easy to use. it has a 12cm long cable. It has no warranty.</p></li></ul>', 'en', '2021-07-06 05:56:00', '2021-07-06 05:56:00'),
(202, 201, 'Ducky One 2 SF Mechanical Keyboard', '1 Pcs', '<h2 style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Key Features</h2><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">MPN: DKON1967ST</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Model: One 2 SF</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Anti-Ghosting</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">RGB light effects</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Petite Bezel Design</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Detachable USB Type-C</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\"><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; line-height: 26px;\">Ducky One 2 SF Mechanical Keyboard</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">The new bezel design shares a similar sleek frame as its predecessor, but the One 2 SF incorporates dual colors on the bezel to match all varieties of keycap colorways. We use USB HID with the highest frequency of 1000Hz polling rate, meaning the keyboard is sending its input signal(s) to your PC 1000 times per second. The keyboard utilizes 3528 SMD RGB LED with longer life expectancy &amp; has better signal stability. Handle any number of simultaneous key presses with the option of N-key or 6-Key Rollover. SF stands for Sixty-Five, we bring the groundbreaking size for customers\' choice.</p></li></u