(203, 202, 'Hunter L16 Gaming Mouse Pad', '1 Pcs', '<ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Model: Hunter L16</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Steady, thick, rubberized base</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">A stable, comfortable base</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Mouse Pad Material: Soft</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\"><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; line-height: 26px;\">Hunter L16 Gaming Mouse Pad</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">Steady, thick, rubberized base keeps mouse pad in place and High non-slip rubber, high toughness, the same type, long life, even more firmly seize the Desktop. The diamention of the mouse pad is 30 X 23 X 0.03 cm. Gaming mouse pad are ideal for gamers, graphic designers, or anyone who uses a mouse for long sessions. This large size Mouse pad, Gaming Mouse pad, mouse pad are for pc and laptop.</p></li></ul>', 'en', '2021-07-06 06:01:15', '2021-07-06 06:01:15'),
(204, 203, 'JBL GO 2 Portable Bluetooth Speaker', '1 Pcs', '<h2 style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif;\">Key Features</h2><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">MPN: 3W-JBLGO2BLK</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">Model: JBL GO 2</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">JBL Signature Sound</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">IPX7 Water Proof</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\">5 Hours Playing Time</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; display: block; line-height: 20px;\"><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; line-height: 26px;\">The JBL GO 2 Portable Bluetooth Speaker</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">The JBL GO 2 Portable Bluetooth Speaker has come with a bang. It comes with new and improved technology that helps it to be more mobile, resistant to water and also the design itself is astonishing.The Video Below will provide you with more information about the speaker.</p></li></ul>', 'en', '2021-07-06 06:04:11', '2021-07-06 06:04:11');
